parameters:
"Fun times always fly by so quickly. Before I know it, it's
already evening. I should start heading home soon."

"Getting caught up in conversation after school is becoming
a daily routine. I really want to take Makoto to various
places, but..."

"As long as I'm with Mamoru, I enjoy myself no matter where
we are. Just watching the sunset together like this makes me
feel incredibly happy."

"Ever since I took you to that park, it seems like you've
become fond of watching the sunsets."

"Yes. Because it reminds me of the scenery you showed me
that day. Mamoru, thank you so much for saving me..."

"Helping the person you love is only natural, right? If I
were stronger, maybe I could have looked a bit cooler..."

"No, you were the coolest person to me at that time. Mamoru,
you're my prince. I love you so much, Mamoru..."

"I love you too... Let's always be together, forever and
ever, Makoto."

"Fun times always fly by so quickly. Before I know it, it's
already evening. I should start heading home soon."

"It's becoming a daily routine to get caught up in
conversation after school. I really want to take Makoto to
various places, but..."

"As long as I'm with Mamoru, I enjoy myself no matter where
we are. Just watching the sunset together like this makes me
feel incredibly happy."

"Ever since I took you to that park, it seems like watching
the sunset has become one of your favorite things."

"Yes. It reminds me of the scenery you showed me that day.
Mamoru, thank you so much for saving me..."

"It's only natural to help someone you love, right? If I
were stronger, maybe I could have looked a bit cooler..."

"No, you were the coolest person at that moment. Mamoru,
you're my prince. I love you, Mamoru..."

"I love you too... Let's always be together, forever and
ever, Makoto."

"The sky is so clear and it feels great. It was definitely
the right decision to borrow the rooftop key."

"Normally, I don't think you'd be able to borrow it even if
you asked... Maybe it's because of your good nature, Makoto,
or perhaps because you're the young lady of the Asahi
family."

"Hehe, maybe it's both. Well then, let's go ahead and have
lunch."

"We promised to exchange lunch boxes today, after all. I
made lots of your favorite dishes, Mamoru."

"Wow, I'm so happy. I also made some of your favorites,
Makoto. Hey, how about we feed each other the first bite?"

"Ah, that's embarrassing. But I might want to try it...♡
Okay, let's do it together? Ready... Ahh~♡"

Ah, I'm truly happy. It's like living a dream every day. But
this happiness isn't just for today. Our peaceful days will
continue on forever.
